---
sequenceDiagram
    participant H3 as host_03 (test client)
    participant VIP as VLAN VIP 172.16.1.100
    participant H1 as host_01 (primary)
    participant H2 as host_02 (secondary)

    Note over H1,H2: Normal operation — host_01 owns VIP
    H3->>VIP: ping 172.16.1.100
    VIP->>H1: delivered to primary
    H1-->>H3: reply

    Note over H1,H2: Failover — Keepalived stopped on host_01
    H1->>H2: VRRP heartbeat lost
    H2->>VIP: takes VIP ownership
    H3->>VIP: ping 172.16.1.100
    VIP->>H2: delivered to new primary
    H2-->>H3: reply

    Note over H1,H2: Recovery — Keepalived restarted on host_01
    H1->>H2: VRRP heartbeats restored
    H1->>VIP: resumes VIP ownership
    H2->>VIP: demotes to standby
